      "description": "",
      "id": "awsDatabaseMigrationSvc_serverless",
      "helpText": {
        "aws": "AWS Database Migration Service Serverless automatically adjusts capacity based on need. DMS Serverless is priced in DMS Capacity Units (DCUs). One DCU is equal to 2GB RAM. It is recommended that customers choose the largest DCU maximum capacity setting to allow the greatest benefit from auto-scaling to accommodate spikes in transaction volume. The pricing calculator shows the maximum monthly cost if continuously replicating at the maximum DCU. This does not represent the actual cost, as you only pay for the capacity used.",
        "aws-cn": "Amazon Web Services Database Migration Service Serverless automatically adjusts capacity based on need. DMS Serverless is priced in DMS Capacity Units (DCUs). One DCU is equal to 2GB RAM. It is recommended that customers choose the largest DCU maximum capacity setting to allow the greatest benefit from auto-scaling to accommodate spikes in transaction volume. The pricing calculator shows the maximum monthly cost if continuously replicating at the maximum DCU. This does not represent the actual cost, as you only pay for the capacity used."
      },
